Half-Orc Siblings
d%Result
01—601d6+1 orc siblings. You gain access to the Kin Guardian combat trait.
61—701d4 human siblings. With two or more siblings, you gain access to the Kin Guardian combat trait.
71—80One half-orc sibling.
81—100No siblings.
